                     <interp inst="t17860111-41-verdict199" type="verdictSubcategory" value="lesserOffence"></interp>
               GUILTY Of stealing, but not privately
            </rs>.</p>

               <p>
                  <rs id="t17860111-41-punish200" type="punishmentDescription">
